455
01:23:14 --> 01:23:24
BOD YGUARD:
They brought the body.

456
01:23:25 --> 01:23:35
So, dead, that's 500.

457
01:23:36 --> 01:23:46
How about alive? Hm?

458
01:23:47 --> 01:23:57
You wanna know how I got these scars?

459
01:23:58 --> 01:24:08
My father was...

460
01:24:09 --> 01:24:19
...a drinker...

461
