512
01:33:41 --> 01:33:51
Sends out a high-frequency pulse...

513
01:33:52 --> 01:34:02
...records the response time
for mapping an environment.

514
01:34:03 --> 01:34:13
Sonar. Just like a...

515
01:34:14 --> 01:34:24
Submarine, Mr. Wayne.
Like a submarine.

516
01:34:25 --> 01:34:35
- And the other device?
- It's in place.

517
01:34:36 --> 01:34:46
Mr. Wayne?

518
01:34:47 --> 01:34:57
Good luck.

519
01:34:58 --> 01:35:08
[SPEAKING IN CHINESE]

