01:35:53 --> 01:36:03
[SIRENS WAILING]

525
01:36:04 --> 01:36:14
[CHATTERING IN CHINESE]

526
01:36:15 --> 01:36:25
[LAU SHOUTING IN CHINESE]

527
01:36:26 --> 01:36:36
[ENGINES RUMBLING]

